<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefab607b-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s308304"><num value="308304">§ 308304.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idefab607c-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s308304/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Amounts</inline>.—</heading><chapeau>There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out this chapter $2,500,000 for each fiscal year, of which—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefab607d-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s308304/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $2,000,000 shall be used to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t54/s308302">section 308302 of this title</ref>; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefab607e-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s308304/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $500,000 shall be used to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t54/s308303">section 308303 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idefab607f-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s308304/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Limitation</inline>.—</heading><content>No amount may be appropriated for the purposes of this chapter except to the Secretary for carrying out the responsibilities of the Secretary as set forth in this chapter.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idefab6080-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3235">128 Stat. 3235</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
